my era was the fact that as fish you went through a 
very tough year in which you shared a lot of

21:19.223 --> 21:34.964
experiences, some of which were painful and some, 
though, which you had a lot of fun doing. And that, I

21:36.146 --> 21:45.298
think that, plus the fact that you were they 
emphasized, I'd say, duty on a country, which you

21:45.278 --> 21:58.081
never forgot. And

21:58.101 --> 22:08.099
that bonding is somewhat different than other 
schools. Are there some key the events of being in

22:10.439 --> 22:13.184
the Corps and so forth. But are there some other 
